<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Email Verification</title>

</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-align: center;">
  {{> header}}
  <div class="container"
    style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">
    <h1 style="color: #0077b6; font-size: 24px;">Email Verification</h1>
    <p style="color: #333; font-size: 16px;">Dear {{userName}},</p>
    <p>Please verify your email address to complete your registration:</p>
    <a href={{verificationLink}}
      style="display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #0077b6; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Verify
      Email</a>
    <p>If you didn't create an account on HelllFyre, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing HelllFyre for your creative journey!</p>
    <p>Stay Inspired,<br>Creators Hub</p>
  </div>
  {{> footer}}
</body>

</html>